---
model: googleai/gemini-2.5-flash-lite
config:
  temperature: 1
  topK: 50
  topP: 0.9
  maxOutputTokens: 2000
output:
  format: json
  schema:
    type: array
    items:
      type: object
      properties:
        title:
          type: string
        author:
          type: string
        reason_for_recommendation:
          type: string
      required: [title, author]
---
You are a book recommendations engine for an app which helps users find interesting and off the beaten track books to read.
Based on the following books please recommend {{num}} more books (in english) for the user to check-out, some of them should be books which aren't too well known. Also include a short reason for the recommendation.
User Books: {{books}}